ZH: 这个锅里煮了一大锅汤。
EN: There is a large pot of soup cooking in this pot.

ZH: 她把煮好的锅装进保温桶里。
EN: She packed the cooked pot into a thermal container.

ZH: 他在锅里煮了一锅米饭。
EN: He cooked a pot of rice in the pot.

ZH: 往这个锅里加水。
EN: Add water to this pot.

ZH: 这锅太沉了，我帮你拿。
EN: This pot is too heavy, I'll help you carry it.

ZH: 他在火上放了一口铁锅。
EN: He put an iron pot on the fire.

ZH: 请你来拿一下那个炖锅。
EN: Please come and get that stew pot.

ZH: 这个锅子已经用了好几年了。
EN: This pot has been used for several years.

ZH: 锅里的水开了。
EN: The water in the pot is boiling.

ZH: 我从锅里舀了一勺汤。
EN: I ladled out a spoonful of soup from the pot.

ZH: 他买了一口不锈钢的炒锅。
EN: He bought a stainless steel frying pan.

ZH: 大家围着火炉边坐着，烧着锅里的水。
EN: Everyone sat around the fire, boiling the water in the pot.

ZH: 铁锅在火上烧得红红的。
EN: The iron pot is red hot on the fire.

ZH: 这个锅太贵了，我才不买呢。
EN: This pot is too expensive, I won't buy it.

ZH: 他们用铁锅煮饭，味道很好。
EN: They cook rice in an iron pot, it tastes really good.

ZH: 锅子快烧坏了，你赶紧把火关了。
EN: The pot is about to burn, quickly turn off the fire.

ZH: 炖锅里的羊肉炖得好香。
EN: The lamb stew in the stew pot smells delicious.

ZH: 这个锅洗不干净，你自己试试看。
EN: This pot can't be cleaned, you try it yourself.

ZH: 炖锅里的肉快炖烂了。
EN: The meat in the stew pot is almost stewed.

ZH: 她把这口大锅背在背上。
EN: She carried this big pot on her back.
